description:
We're going to go back in time to a remarkable scene on the plains of Dura right near ancient Babylon.  An enormous statue of King Nebuchadnezzar had been set up, and thousands of representatives from his empire were invited to pay homage to it in a splendid ceremony.  But when the vast assembly on the plain bowed to the ground toward the image, three young men defied the king and remained standing. Their decision angered a king and shook an empire.  Its also encouraged people everywhere. This is their story.
